Deck 生效。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：FCC&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：FCC&lt;/cite>; &lt;/图>; &lt;p id=&quot;YGVFVK&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification&quot;>;经过韩国国家无线电研究机构审查的神秘“Valve 1030”现已在美国被明确认定为 Steam Deck，这是我们第一个证明该硬件可能足够接近发布，以证明有必要向其他人展示它。监管机构。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MoJH7M&quot;>;为什么我们现在才知道这一点？因为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification#:~:text=Valve%20management%20to %20get%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20past%20the%20FCC%20without%20being%20spotted%20early%2C%20by%20having%20its%20Wi%2DFi%20/%20Bluetooth%20vendor%20Realtek%20re%2Dcertify%20the% 20wireless%20module%20rather%20than%20certifying%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20itself。&quot;>;就像最初的 Steam Deck&lt;/a>; 一样，Valve 使用其 Wi-Fi 和蓝牙芯片供应商来偷偷通过。阀门侦探 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SadlyItsBradley/status/1709644205084021226&quot;>;布拉德...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry></feed>